{"type":"message","id":"ddd0d9d4","parentId":"586a7d89","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:21:34.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到了飞书APP的权限。让我分析一下关键权限：\n\n**已授予的权限 (tenant级别):**\n- `im:message` - 发消息权限\n- `im:message:send_as_bot` - 以机器人身份发送消息\n- `im:message:readonly` - 读取消息\n- `im:message.p2p_msg:readonly` - 读取P2P消息\n- `im:message.group_at_msg:readonly` - 读取群消息\n- `im:chat.members:bot_access` - 机器人访问群成员\n- `im:chat.access_event.bot_p2p_chat:read` - 读取机器人P2P聊天事件\n- `im:resource` - 资源上传下载\n- `aily:file:read` / `aily:file:write` - 文件读写\n- `contact:contact.base:readonly` - 联系人只读\n\n**用户级别权限:**\n- `base:record:read` - 读取Bitable记录\n- `space:document.event:read` - 读取文档事件\n- `docs:permission.member:create` - 创建文档权限成员\n- `sheets:spreadsheet` - 电子表格\n\n现在让我测试这些功能：\n\n1. **主动给联系人发信息** - 需要获取当前用户ID，然后发消息\n2. **群内发信息** - 需要获取群ID，然后发消息\n3. **上传飞书云文档** - 需要创建文档\n\n\n4. **定时任务** - 需要检查cron配置\n\n让我先获取当前用户信息，然后开始测试。","thinkingSignature":"734bf8a95e38f9a34208bb95952b5f56cbf07ac3ac6f2e4cf931a4e0e24bac83"},{"type":"text","text":"权限看起来挺全的。让我开始测试！\n\n首先获取当前飞书用户信息：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yupecd4fcl3v_1","name":"feishu_wiki","arguments":{"action":"spaces"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":914,"output":382,"cacheRead":14618,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15914,"cost":{"input":0.0005484,"output":0.0009168,"cacheRead":0.0008770799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023422799999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772270489302}}
